node.text: What if you could bring entire worlds into being with the power of your mind? Moondragon has arrived!

node.text: Introduced in Iron Man issue 54 back in 1973, Moondragon uses her psionic abilities to tear through the minds of her opponents. In the comics, she now serves as a member of the Guardians of the Galaxy with her partner Phyla-Vell, battling psychic powerhouses like the Universal Church of Truth. #MARVEL #MARVELStrikeForce #MARVELgames #GuardiansoftheGalaxy #Moondragon #PhylaVell #StarLord #AdamWarlock #Groot #SilverSurfer #Nova #CosmicGhostRider #betaraybill

node.text: Moondragon is one of the most powerful telepaths in the MARVEL Universe. Now name 3 others.
